- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper uses data from location-based social networks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning techniques for recommendation. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is unlikely as the paper is not related to sound or audio processing.
